i created my github account
then i install git and add permission using this commands:
sudo dnf install git-all
git config --global user.name "alaa-abouzied"
git config --global user.email "alaa.m.abouzied@gmail.com"
git config --global init.defaultBranch main

then created ssh
ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C "alaa.m.abouzied@gmail.com"
then i added it
-------------------------------------------------------
to clone create directory
1) create directory
   $mkdir alaa
2)make it the current directory
   $cd alaa
3)git clone
    $git clone git@github.com:FatmaKhaled/repopythonm.git
4)then create file
    $touch alaa
5)add all changes to the sataging area
    $git add .
6)commit all changes to the local server
    $git commit -m "this file to explain the steps to push remotly"
7)to install any updates
     $git pull origin main
8)push all commits to remote server
    $git push origin main
---------------------------------------------------------
